Package: PSInetR
Type: Package
Title: Access Plant Water Potential Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Keaton", "Wilson", email = "keatonwilson@me.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to access and work with plant water potential data
    from various sources. Allows downloading data from repositories or Zenodo, and
    includes utilities for data validation and manipulation.
